  "title": "A small round UFO spotted orbiting a bigger one near Cachoeirinha [2005]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/08/a-small-round-ufo-spotted-orbiting-a-bigger-one-near-cachoeirinha-2005/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-hx",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JAN 26th, 2005</strong>. Time: 10:30 am. Duration: 5 minutes. In Cachoeirinha, a city in the state of Rio Grande do Sul, a witness spotted two unidentified flying objects under clear skies and favorable visibility. According to the witness, the two UFOs were round and bright, and looked like the planet Venus. The objects also moved in a peculiar way: the &#8220;smaller object, grayish in color, [was] more opaque, with circular movements, following the movement of the larger one, orbiting it.&#8221;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.650. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Ocorrência de tráfego hotel em Cachoeirinha, Rio Grande do Sul&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
